==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nitrated
<hw>Ni"tra*ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Combined, or impregnated, with nitric acid, or
some of its compounds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Photog.)</fld> <def>Prepared with silver
nitrate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nitratine</ent>⟦br⟧
